&lt;p&gt;The Northumberland and North Tyneside psychiatric liaison services require band 6 practitioners to join the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a 24/7 service working onsite at local acute trust in Northumberland, providing mental health assessments and interventions for all ages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a dynamic team, motivated and supportive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a mental health emergency department in response to Covid.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be based at NSECH and working with service users who are predominately 16- 65 years, and there is an opportunities to do joint assessments with children&#39;s nurses and older adult nurses, developing your skills in other areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;for further details contact&lt;/p&gt;
